insert into "products" ("body_html", "created_at", "handle", "id", "image", "images", "options", "product_type", "published_at", "published_scope", "tags", "template_suffix", "title", "metafields_global_title_tag", "metafields_global_description_tag", "updated_at", "variants", "vendor") values ('The Timber ridge family cabin tent creates a literal home away from home, with a comfortable walk-in 2 room, straight walled, high ceiling design. With 160 square feet of area, the Timber Ridge sleeps up to 10 people comfortably; or provides sleep and indoor living space for smaller groups. The tent is well ventilated with nearly an 8 foot center height, two large mesh Dutch D doors, front, back, and side zippered windows for privacy, and a fully vented roof. In wet weather the Timber Ridge full coverage rainfly and welded polyethylene floor provides the protection you need to stay dry. In clear weather, roll the fly back and enjoy stargazing from the insect protected interior. Amazingly easy to set up for such large and stable tent, the Timber Ridge features a central hub that connect the fiberglass roof structure to steel uprights and a simple to use fast feet system. Equipped with an E-port for electrical cords and two hanging pockets, the Timber Ridge makes it easy to keep larger groups organized. The Timber Ridge comes complete with steel stakes for secure placement, attached guy ropes for additional stability, and a convenient travel storage duffel.Wenzel Timber Ridge 10 Person Tent

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
